# Build Workflow

## Commands

```bash
npm start          # Watch mode (dev build + BrowserSync)
npm run dev        # Same as npm start
npm run build      # Production build (NODE_ENV=production)
npm run sass       # Compile SCSS only
npm run js         # Compile JS only
npm run build:dev  # Dev build (no watch, no server)
```

## Gulp Tasks (gulpfile.mjs)

| Task | Input | Output | Notes |
|---|---|---|---|
| `sassTask` | `src/sass/style.scss` | `style.css` | Main stylesheet |
| `blockSassTask` | `blocks/**/*.scss` | `blocks/**/*.css` (in-place) | Per-block styles |
| `customJsTask` | `src/js/custom/**/*.js` | `assets/js/custom.js` | Concat, DOMContentLoaded wrapped |
| `pluginsJsTask` | `src/js/plugins/*.js` | `assets/js/plugins.js` | Simple concat |
| `swiperJsTask` | `src/js/swiper-init.js` | `assets/js/swiper-bundle.js` | esbuild bundle |
| `imagesTask` | source images | `assets/images/` | Sharp optimization |
| `webpTask` | source images | `assets/images/` | WebP conversion |
| `purgeCSSTask` | style.css | purged style.css | Production only |
| `rtlCssTask` | style.css | style-rtl.css | RTL stylesheet |

## PostCSS Pipeline

- **Dev**: autoprefixer + sort-media-queries
- **Prod**: autoprefixer + sort-media-queries + cssnano (minify)

## Manual Block SCSS Compilation

When not using Gulp watch:

```bash
npx sass blocks/{slug}/{slug}.scss blocks/{slug}/{slug}.css --no-source-map
```

## Asset Enqueueing (functions/enqueue-scripts.php)

- Block CSS/JS only loaded when block exists on page (`has_block()`)
- CSS versioned by `filemtime()` for cache busting
- Block JS gets `defer` attribute automatically
- Block JS depends on `skel-swiper` script handle

## JS File Pipeline

| Source | Output | Method |
|---|---|---|
| `src/js/plugins/*.js` | `assets/js/plugins.js` | Gulp concat |
| `src/js/custom/*.js` | `assets/js/custom.js` | Gulp concat (DOMContentLoaded wrapped) |
| `src/js/swiper-init.js` | `assets/js/swiper-bundle.js` | esbuild bundle |
| `blocks/{slug}/{slug}.js` | (loaded directly) | Enqueued conditionally per-page |
